# =============================================================================
# Important Notes
# =============================================================================

# - This tool processes images sequentially with delays to respect VSCO's terms
# - Authentication is optional but may provide access to higher quality images
# - The tool uses VSCO's public endpoints and browser automation, not private APIs
# - Always respect VSCO's terms of service and image creators' rights
# - Image quality depends on what VSCO serves publicly vs. to authenticated users
